{"type":"message","id":"f5ac2b52","parentId":"141e70f0","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:18:47.134Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ca80a3819150483cbe92ba3f","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 137 ## 3:54 PM (L1 Discussion Review)\n 138 - Read L1 discussion docs: node-management.md, app-management.md, overview.md\n 139 - Allan clarified: L1 should only handle ledger + sync, L2 handles verification/registration\n 140 \n-141 ## 4:00 PM (Node Join Process Redesign)\n+141 ## 4:02 PM (Heartbeat Check)\n+142 - Checked TODO.md — still working on L1 node join process with Allan\n+143 - No new messages from Allan yet\n+144 \n+145 ## 4:17 PM (Still Waiting)\n 142 - Proposed new architecture: nodes register via L2 app, L1 just stores ledger\n 143 - Similar to app pattern: L2 registration → verification → promoted to L1\n 144 - Waiting for Allan's feedback\n 145 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":141},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773649127130}}
