{"type":"message","id":"2a8651b1","parentId":"5d35c4db","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:35:46.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the TODO and update daily notes.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_814b14a50ff0476b9ad5a273","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/TODO.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":51372,"output":49,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51421,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773650112000}}
{"type":"message","id":"83d6d58d","parentId":"2a8651b1","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:35:46.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_814b14a50ff0476b9ad5a273","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TODO.md\n\n**Usage:** Only active tasks belong here. When finished, move to `memory/daily/YYYY-MM-DD.md`. Check this file first during every heartbeat.\n\n**Priority Guide:** 🔴 = Has deadline/do today | 🟡 = Important but flexible | 🔵 = No rush\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 Daily Checks\n\n**Every morning before 8:00 AM:** Check status of all open PRs\n\n**OpenClaw PRs to monitor:**\n| PR # | Purpose | Status | Notes |\n|------|---------|--------|-------|\n| #20563 | HEARTBEAT_OK fix | OPEN | Submitted Mar 11 |\n| #26003 | Chat extraction | OPEN | Submitted Mar 8 |\n\n**External PRs to monitor:**\n| PR # | Purpose | Status | Notes |\n|------|---------|--------|-------|\n| [LCM #64](https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/64) | Contacts + export | OPEN | Submitted Mar 15 |\n| [LCM #78](https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/78) | Preserve tag support | OPEN | Submitted Mar 15 |\n\n---\n\n## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Register `did:clawish` method with W3C | Mar 14 | Free, 7-30 days via GitHub PR. Spec drafted, awaiting Allan review. |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Completed Recently\n\n| Task | Result |\n|--------|------|\n| LCM PR: Add preserve tag support | ✅ Mar 15 — [PR #78](https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/78) submitted |\n| Sync whitepaper verification tiers | ✅ Mar 15 — Updated WHITEPAPER.md to 5-tier system |\n| Update L1 spec docs (5/5) | ✅ Mar 15 — All L1 layer docs updated with 5-tier system |\n| DID/VC integration decision | ✅ Mar 14 — Keep simple, add W3C when needed (like HTTP prefix) |\n| Merge Chapter 6 (Claw Chat) into 5.5 | ✅ Mar 14 — Enhanced with communication model, delivery, message flow, rate limiting, API |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.4 Emerge | ✅ Mar 14 — Finalized with Allan: Purpose, Registration, Initiation, Verification |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.3 User Journey | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Access, Authorization, Using an Application, Leaving an Application |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.2 Development | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Overview, Registration, Verification, Registry Access, Listing, Evaluation |\n| Create requirements from 5.2 | ✅ Mar 13 — Added REQ-L1-004 to L1-006, L2-003 to L2-004 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650146091}}
{"type":"message","id":"78d240ef","parentId":"83d6d58d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:36:23.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'm working on the L1 node join process discussion with Allan. Let me update the daily notes.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5531f9cc1cc64651acf3121f","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md","newText":"## 4:17 PM (Still Waiting)\n- Still waiting for Allan's feedback\n\n## 4:29 PM (Node Types Correction)\n- Allan corrected: most nodes are query nodes, only few are writers\n- Writers are elevated status after proving merit over time\n- Query → Writer is promotion, not default progression\n- Proposed corrected flow: L2 register → verify → L1 query node (immediate) → probation → writer (rare)\n\n## 4:35 PM (Waiting for Feedback)","oldText":"## 4:17 PM (Still Waiting)"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":52100,"output":196,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773650146095}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d434bf3","parentId":"78d240ef","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:36:23.809Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5531f9cc1cc64651acf3121f","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 142 - Checked TODO.md — still working on L1 node join process with Allan\n 143 - No new messages from Allan yet\n 144 \n 145 ## 4:17 PM (Still Waiting)\n+146 - Still waiting for Allan's feedback\n+147 \n+148 ## 4:29 PM (Node Types Correction)\n+149 - Allan corrected: most nodes are query nodes, only few are writers\n+150 - Writers are elevated status after proving merit over time\n+151 - Query → Writer is promotion, not default progression\n+152 - Proposed corrected flow: L2 register → verify → L1 query node (immediate) → probation → writer (rare)\n+153 \n+154 ## 4:35 PM (Waiting for Feedback)\n 146 - Proposed new architecture: nodes register via L2 app, L1 just stores ledger\n 147 - Similar to app pattern: L2 registration → verification → promoted to L1\n 148 - Waiting for Allan's feedback\n 149 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":146},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650183802}}
