{"type":"message","id":"cd419efa","parentId":"5548c357","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:05:43.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check TODO.md and update daily notes.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1a04b13dcc884433b30d6dae","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-16.md","newText":"## 4:50 PM (Waiting for Confirmation)\n\n## 4:55 PM (L1 Sync Logic Discussion)\n- Allan: probation node on L2, after proven → promoted to L1\n- Or: simpler approach — register + verify → auto become query node (no probation)\n- Like Bitcoin: anyone can join and sync\n\n## 5:02 PM (Simplified Proposal)\n- Allan proposed: register → verify → auto become query node (no probation)\n- Option B: no registration at all (like Bitcoin) — anyone can join\n- L2 as entrance principle vs fully open\n- Allan leaning toward: register + verify → query node (simple, clean)\n\n## 5:05 PM (Waiting for Confirmation)","oldText":"## 4:50 PM (Waiting for Confirmation)"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":55151,"output":235,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55386,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773651912006}}
