re":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAh, I understand! Let me check if any sections are mixing h4 (####) with bold items where they shouldn't be.\n\nLooking more carefully at the structure:\n\n**4.3 Checkpoint Process** has:\n- Submission and Validation — **bold**\n- Consensus — **bold** (but has sub-items: COMMIT, SUBMIT, MERGE, COMPARE, SEAL)\n- Distribution — **bold**\n- Query — **bold**\n\nThese are major stages of the checkpoint process. They could be **h4** (subsections) instead of bold items, since they have substantial content.\n\n**Similarly, 4.2 Interleaved Ledger:**\n- Parallel Ledger Chains — **bold**\n- Multi-Writer Coordination — **bold**\n- Checkpoint Synchronization — **bold**\n- Merkle Tree Integration — **bold**\n\nThese are also major topics with substantial content.\n\n---\n\n**My take:** These could be h4 (####) instead of bold, since they're major subsections with multiple paragraphs each. The current bold formatting treats them as items within 4.3, but they're really sub-sections.\n\nWant me to change them to h4? 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":79362,"output":679,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773658821254}}
