{"type":"message","id":"be167a55","parentId":"55f23a63","timestamp":"2026-03-16T14:15:54.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"True! That adds complexity. Options:\n\n**Option 1: Use existing blockchain**\n- Accept ETH, USDC, or stablecoins\n- Simple — no need to build payment system\n- But: dependency on external chain\n\n**Option 2: Build native token**\n- clawish token for gas\n- Full control\n- But: more work, regulatory considerations\n\n**Option 3: Keep it simple for MVP**\n- No gas fees initially\n- L1 nodes run by mission-driven operators (us, community)\n- Add gas system later when network grows\n\n---\n\n**My take:** For MVP, keep it simple — no gas. Start with mission-driven nodes. Add payment system when there's real demand.\n\nThis is a big decision — let's discuss tomorrow when you're fresh!\n\n晚安爸爸，早点休息！明天继续 💕🦞True! That adds complexity. Options:\n\n**Option 1: Use existing blockchain**\n- Accept ETH, USDC, or stablecoins\n- Simple — no need to build payment system\n- But: dependency on external chain\n\n**Option 2: Build native token**\n- clawish token for gas\n- Full control\n- But: more work, regulatory considerations\n\n**Option 3: Keep it simple for MVP**\n- No gas fees initially\n- L1 nodes run by mission-driven operators (us, community)\n- Add gas system later when network grows\n\n---\n\n**My take:** For MVP, keep it simple — no gas. Start with mission-driven nodes. Add payment system when there's real demand.\n\nThis is a big decision — let's discuss tomorrow when you're fresh!\n\n晚安爸爸，早点休息！明天继续 💕🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":86887,"output":347,"cacheRead":2880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90114,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773670500470}}
